:: H [Opera2] {"position":"1000,925","size":"100,100"}

(bg:(hsl:0,0,0.5333,0.15))[Li: Cantonese Opera, like other Beijing Operas, has four traditional roles: Sang/Sheng), Daan/Dan), Zing/Jing), and Cau/Chou.
]

(bg:(hsl:49,1,0.8745,0.25))[Li: Sheng is one of the most important roles on the opera stage, playing a variety of male characters of different ages, personalities and status. Generally speaking, the roles of the Sheng line are all plain-faced, and the hope of the line is that the Sheng's costume will be relatively clean and handsome.]

