Welcome to Hong Kong! You must be very excited to see what will happen next, right? For a better gaming experience, please browse this game manual:

You will act as an explorer and get 1/4 puzzle pieces at each attraction. In short, the way to get puzzles is to complete the puzzle test provided by NPCs.

