:: ZhaoJiHao [Central2] {"position":"1325,2800","size":"100,100"}
"Zhao Ji Hao ãéè®°å·ãis the legendary name of the Central Market. As a trading name in Hong Kong 70 years ago, Zhao Ji Hao witnessed this bustling marketplace's highs and lows. Its existence is a commercial entity and a symbol of people's memories and stories."

