[Chow Chun Fai was born in 1980 and lives in Hong Kong. Fai graduated from the Chinese University of Hong Kong with a B.A. and M.A. degree, where he currently teaches painting.  In his latest series of "Movie Paintings", Fai depicts animated transitions and matching subtitles from classic Hong Kong films of the New Wave Cinema movement as well as more recent, internationally acclaimed films. ]

