src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/TYXhRibMtQR0yV2YWPrt0Eciag0BQlGhxFFtYvdgEwdeNTp0vCsDnEZ8FDBTs215qiaONPwafTgy7RWiazcty9gPRw/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1
" style="Max-width:100%; Max-height:100%">


"To hold on to the collective memories for citizens, the pots of many plants in the interior were designed as stacked steamers. "


